    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kaskade 是一款关于连接不断演变的配送网络的极简策略游戏。它旨在让玩家进入专注的“心流”状态，并用最少的工具描绘出一幅图景。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285530/extras/b2cb90f9e3d52d4989979faa22a8d544.poster.avif?t=1750856296\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285530/extras/b2cb90f9e3d52d4989979faa22a8d544.webm?t=1750856296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285530/extras/b2cb90f9e3d52d4989979faa22a8d544.mp4?t=1750856296\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将颜色匹配的输入与输出连接来获得积分。使用积分解锁新的能力。利用这些新能力来更有效地管理你的网络。重复这一过程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285530/extras/f9795112654dc49c643daee175a74597.poster.avif?t=1750856296\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285530/extras/f9795112654dc49c643daee175a74597.webm?t=1750856296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285530/extras/f9795112654dc49c643daee175a74597.mp4?t=1750856296\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >永久死亡！错误太多就会导致游戏结束！没有存档系统，但在每次游玩之间会有类Roguelite的进度保留。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285530/extras/0894e47d6980bd3c9173e065968517e6.poster.avif?t=1750856296\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285530/extras/0894e47d6980bd3c9173e065968517e6.webm?t=1750856296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285530/extras/0894e47d6980bd3c9173e065968517e6.mp4?t=1750856296\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一次禅意的解谜体验或一次策略性的 Roguelite 挑战</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >包含独特机制的 5 个章节</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >三种游戏模式：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >普通模式：体验经典的 Kaskade 玩法，</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无限模式：在无压力沙盒中畅玩，</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >困难模式：面对更严峻的挑战</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可解锁的关键能力（Jump、Double Jump、Switch、Compact、Pause）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >购买增益和升级，以管理越来越多的配送</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >色盲模式（配送有清晰的标签）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >支持鼠标和键盘（不推荐使用游戏手柄）</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
